{"tid":925481,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"麥浚龍既歌喺夜晚聽真係好撚攞命","createTime":"2018-12-02T18:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T21:48:59.000Z","uid":170867,"like":312,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"82291219e927ee1ff32e695ab23711b74f05989c","tid":925481,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"讓我們打聽對方天天過得一切平安<br />\n縱使相見已是路人茫茫 這生恐怕會念念你不放<br />\n<br />\n那感情戲 並未存在過<br />\n那小火花卻讓我 過敏地回應太多<br />\n<br />\n我有時還會妄想 她一樣放不開<br />\n我倆將來 尚有將來 最後不該 失散於人海<br />\n<br />\n相見是意外 見不到才是應該<br />\n我本可以分得開 看得開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我可以為你點一點火 然後望你輪廓<br />\n不講甚麼悲壯 不想甚麼沮喪<br />\n<br />\n盆栽枯死　就缺氧急促喘氣 <br />\n夜半三更都要想你 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首首都痴撚線 世界級"},{"pid":"b2951e05af081a6943c6950fd8e1bb8d9205eef9","tid":925481,"uid":179645,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:37:37.000Z","msg":"你那金剛圈 最好箍得更緊"},{"pid":"0652680b68be69ca6977c916ce7fd3ccc0557618","tid":925481,"uid":170867,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"b2951e05af081a6943c6950fd8e1bb8d9205eef9","tid":925481,"uid":179645,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:37:37.000Z","msg":"你那金剛圈 最好箍得更緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:38:41.000Z","msg":"令我的下世 記得有過今生"},{"pid":"e7ca35d5a4df7326261fb3af0493af6691ddb9dc","tid":925481,"uid":20073,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"0652680b68be69ca6977c916ce7fd3ccc0557618","tid":925481,"uid":170867,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"b2951e05af081a6943c6950fd8e1bb8d9205eef9","tid":925481,"uid":179645,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:37:37.000Z","msg":"你那金剛圈 最好箍得更緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:38:41.000Z","msg":"令我的下世 記得有過今生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:48:16.000Z","msg":"來讓我命運 和你箍緊"},{"pid":"0ed9f2017b82f259ef8da5504ba6cbcfd63f9c7d","tid":925481,"uid":170867,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"e7ca35d5a4df7326261fb3af0493af6691ddb9dc